<!--
  Bibliography of the book.
  - bib-rosen-2019 is the primary English source.
  - The remaining entries are the Vietnamese corpus (terminology sources),
    seeded from the Zotero "Discrete Math" collection. Each carries its Zotero
    item key in a comment for provenance (data/sources/registry.yaml is the
    machine-readable registry). Publisher/place fields are to be enriched in
    Phase 1.
-->
